   <topic>CURRENT_RECORD Function</topic>
    <description>Returns the current record number</description>
   
   
   <prototype>RecNum as N = current_record()</prototype>
  
   <example><![CDATA[
dim ptr as P
ptr = form.view("Travel Time")
ptr.Fetch_Last()
? current_record()
= 159.000000
]]></example>
   
